{"tid":1433404,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］黑社會的弱點","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:19:36.000Z","uid":94441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"abf2ff1dbc01d4e187f01e282fa0a6224767db53","tid":1433404,"uid":94441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"部分黑社會着嘅軍裝鞋，防滑能力甚差，極怕地滑。<br />\n<br />\n而香港餐廳往往會有廢油（炸到變哂色的油），餐廳往往需要俾錢回收公司回收廢油。<br />\n<br />\n如果有人可以幫餐廳免費處理廢油就好喇！<br />\n<br />\n前線後退，不再推回戰線時，留下一地油水（油水1:1），咪話黑社會唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17400754e55632d0b24e07657041ba4fed891cfb","tid":1433404,"uid":94441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓豬好陰毒"},{"pid":"8426d258a35549cb6d607ce9360307fb79398640","tid":1433404,"uid":94441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該可行，又可以減輕餐廳支出"},{"pid":"69bd56bd743e3b8b7d3436e0b86048d7c848f1e2","tid":1433404,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:12:17.000Z","msg":"起火點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07069fc328ee30d5d636f51f166d0ec4f10daf8e","tid":1433404,"uid":94441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"69bd56bd743e3b8b7d3436e0b86048d7c848f1e2","tid":1433404,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:12:17.000Z","msg":"起火點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:19:36.000Z","msg":"加左水 難起火"}]}